                        body: 'If procedures, suspicious lesions, or dermoscopy are likely, the shortest useful route is no longer remote and should move to booking.',
                        href: '/en/?service=consulta#citas',
                        cta: 'Go to booking',
                        tone: 'fit',
                        target: 'booking',
                    },
                    {
                        step: 'Telemedicine',
                        title: 'When photos and video still improve decision quality',
                        body: 'The current route works best for acne, dermatitis, spots, and follow-ups where visual evidence shapes the next step.',
                        href: '#route-planner',
                        cta: 'Review remote route',
                        tone: 'review',
